welcome_message_body: Welcome to Germantown, where historic charm meets modern convenience! Explore our quaint downtown, known for its charming shops and delicious dining options, and enjoy all that our vibrant city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is reserved for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Washington Dulles International Airport serves as the primary hub for all airlines and provides a variety of services and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Washington Dulles International Airport is home to many domestic and international airlines, offering a range of dining and shopping options for passengers.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Washington Dulles International Airport is primarily used by United Airlines and its alliance partners, providing a variety of services and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at Washington Dulles International Airport is used by a variety of domestic and international airlines, offering a range of dining and shopping options for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but it may require a password or registration.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Frederick Municipal Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Tipton AAF Airport is used exclusively for military flights and operations.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: Terminal A at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves primarily American Airlines and its affiliates.

terminals.name: Terminal B/C
terminals.description: Terminal B/C at Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport serves primarily Delta Air Lines and its affiliates.

wifi.note: Complimentary Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.
